# DEPRECATED — this file is no longer used by iso-sync-local-debs.
#
# iso-sync-local-debs now syncs ALL .debs from foundry-apt/dist/ into
# foundry-iso/local-debs/ automatically before every iso-build. There is no
# longer a hand-curated allowlist — every locally-built package shadows the
# published apt.foundrylinux.org version, so you never get a stale published
# version installed into the ISO by accident.
